Comment Standard
Use /**/
E.G.
// Use "//" for comments that are for testing purposes or will be deleted soon.
// Testing
// Deleted soon

/* Single Line */
/* Normal */

System
E.G.
/* ### Start of [System] ### */
...
/* ### End of [System] ### */

Information
E.G.
/* [TITLE]
 * &: Link, %: File, @: Else
 * &[Link] {[Name]} (...)
 * %[File] {[Path]} (...)
 * @[Else] {...} (...)
 */
/* INFORMATION
 * @[Author] {Facooya} (Founder)
 */
